\v 53 \w and|strong="H3318"\w* \w the|strong="H3318"\w* \w families|strong="H4940"\w* \w of|strong="H4940"\w* \w Kiriath|strong="H7157"\w* Jearim: \w the|strong="H3318"\w* \w Ithrites|strong="H3505"\w*, \w Puthites|strong="H6336"\w*, \w Shumathites|strong="H8126"\w*, \w and|strong="H3318"\w* \w Mishraites|strong="H4954"\w*. \w From|strong="H3318"\w* these \w descended|strong="H3318"\w* \w the|strong="H3318"\w* \w Zorathites|strong="H6882"\w* \w and|strong="H3318"\w* Eshtaolites.
