\p 
\v 28 \w The|strong="H1121"\w* \w sons|strong="H1121"\w* \w of|strong="H1121"\w* Samuel: Joel\f + \fr 6:28 \ft “Joel”: according to some Septuagint manuscripts. The Hebrew text omits this word. See \xt 1 Samuel 8:2\xt*\ft and \xt 1 Chronicles 6:33\xt*\ft .\f* (\w firstborn|strong="H1121"\w*) \w and|strong="H1121"\w* Abijah (second).
\p 
