\v 18 \w Then|strong="H6030"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* Spirit \w came|strong="H1961"\w* \w upon|strong="H5921"\w*\f + \fr 12:18 \ft “Came upon”: literally, “clothed.”\f* Amasai, \w the|strong="H6440"\w* leader \w of|strong="H6440"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* Thirty. “\w We|strong="H7200"\w* \w are|strong="H6440"\w* yours, \w David|strong="H1732"\w*, \w and|strong="H6030"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w are|strong="H6440"\w* \w with|strong="H5921"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w*, son \w of|strong="H6440"\w* Jesse! \w May|strong="H1961"\w* \w peace|strong="H7965"\w*, \w prosperity|strong="H7965"\w*, \w and|strong="H6030"\w* success\f + \fr 12:18 \ft “Peace, prosperity, and success”: literally, “Shalom, shalom to you, and shalom whoever helps you.”\f* \w be|strong="H1961"\w* yours \w and|strong="H6030"\w* \w those|strong="H5921"\w* \w who|strong="H6862"\w* \w help|strong="H5826"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w*, \w for|strong="H5921"\w* \w God|strong="H3808"\w* \w is|strong="H1961"\w* \w the|strong="H6440"\w* \w one|strong="H3808"\w* \w who|strong="H6862"\w* \w is|strong="H1961"\w* \w helping|strong="H5826"\w* \w you|strong="H6440"\w*.” \w So|strong="H1961"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w* allowed \w them|strong="H5921"\w* \w to|strong="H3318"\w* join \w him|strong="H6440"\w*, \w and|strong="H6030"\w* \w put|strong="H3318"\w* \w them|strong="H5921"\w* \w in|strong="H5921"\w* \w charge|strong="H5921"\w* \w of|strong="H6440"\w* \w his|strong="H1732"\w* bands \w of|strong="H6440"\w* raiders.
